text: Namak is the Persian, Urdu and Hindi word for common salt. Namak may also refer to: *Namak, South Korea *Namak-ri *Namaklan-e Olya, Iran *Namaklan-e Sofla, Iran *Namak, Afghanistan *Namak Lake, Iran *Namak (film), a Bollywood film starring Sanjay Dutt ==See also== *Namek *Namakkal *Namakagon (disambiguation)
title: Namak
